<p>【3】Latour, B. (1994). On Technical Mediation. Common Knowledge. Fall Vol.3, no 2. pp. 32-33. </p>
<p>【4】Gillespie, T. (2014). The relevance of algorithms. Media technologies: Essays on communication, materiality, and society, 167(2014), 167. </p>
